  "title": "Senior Pre-Sales Consultant",
  "description": "<p><strong>About fileAI </strong></p><p>fileAI leverages proprietary AI to process any file end-to-end directly into any system without manual intervention. By streamlining repetitive workflows, fileAI enables your team to focus on higher-value tasks and boost productivity.<br /></p><p><strong>How you’ll contribute</strong></p><ul><li><p>Collaborate with Account Executives to understand customer needs and deliver tailored product demonstrations.</p></li><li><p>Own the technical aspects of the sales cycle, including solution design, security reviews, and integration discussions.</p></li><li><p>Lead Proof-of-Concept (PoC) and pilot implementations to showcase product capabilities.</p></li><li><p>Serve as a trusted technical advisor to prospects, addressing questions around architecture, APIs, data security, and scalability.</p></li><li><p>Provide customer feedback to product and engineering teams to help guide roadmap decisions.</p></li><li><p>Create and maintain reusable sales assets such as demo environments, solution diagrams, and technical FAQs.</p></li><li><p>Occasionally support RFP/RFI responses with technical input.</p></li><li><p>Contribute to the development of best practices, templates, and tools to streamline the implementation and delivery process.</p></li><li><p>Maintain strong, ongoing relationships with clients to ensure continued satisfaction and identify opportunities for additional value or upsell.</p></li></ul><p><strong></strong><br /><strong>Who you are</strong></p><ul><li><p>Proven experience in a Pre-Sales, Solutions Engineering, Sales Engineering, or related technical customer-facing role, ideally in an early stage product company</p></li><li><p>Strong understanding of on-premise and cloud technologies (e.g., AWS, Azure, GCP), APIs, and web applications.</p></li><li><p>Familiarity with enterprise IT environments</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Excellent communication and presentation skills, with the ability to tailor messages to both technical and business audiences.</p></li><li><p>Ability to work independently in a fast-paced, ambiguous environment and manage multiple priorities.</p></li><li><p>Hands-on experience with scripting (Python, JavaScript), CRM systems (Salesforce), or BI tools will be an advantage.</p></li></ul><p><br /><strong>Perks & Culture</strong></p><ul><li><p>Competitive salary, performance-based incentives.</p></li><li><p>Health insurance, lunch perks, uncapped leave.</p></li><li><p>Dynamic and collaborative work environment.</p></li><li><p>Grow & learn with a fast-growing organization.</p></li></ul><p><br /><strong>Please submit your application via this form: </strong></p><p><a href=\"https://forms.gle/BC68X3UuMDaMGukm6\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://forms.gle/BC68X3UuMDaMGukm6</a></p>",
